metadata.description: Recently joined to the LKG organization, Yogev release as an inedit version: Fresita (Ft. Danéh). Fresita as his genesis release on sound showcase and electronic style combined with the urban culture where he belongs, first indent song of his style and golden opportunity to join his community backwarded by the Lowkey gang.
